ity of comet 9P/Tempel,\nalthough more work is needed in order to understand to what extent do comets\n9P/Tempel and Hale-Bopp represent comets as a whole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Nov 2008 18:41:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
