)\ncolour. We show that the reliability of the stellar mass content derived with\nthis new estimator for early-type galaxies and its stability are even higher\nthan those achievable with the best classic estimators, with the not negligible\nadvantage that it does not need any multi-wavelength data fitting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Nov 2008 10:00:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
